<b>Hato</b>

250
00:13:24.580 --> 00:13:26.540
<b>(Hato)</b>
<b>Wharf</b>

251
00:13:26.540 --> 00:13:26.580
<b>(Hato)</b>
<b>Wharf</b>

252
